  "prompt": "Can I wear solid colors over camo?",
  "response": "Yes, you can wear solid colors over camo! Layering solid colors over camouflage can create a stylish and balanced look. Choose colors that complement the camouflage pattern, such as neutral tones (black, white, gray) or earthy colors (olive green, brown, tan) for a more cohesive appearance. Just make sure the fit and style work well together for the best effect. Ultimately, fashion is about personal expression, so wear what makes you feel confident!",
